---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Command from "../components/Command.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
---

<Layout title="404: Not Found — Portfolio" description="Lo sentimos, la página que buscas no existe.">
  <main class="container">
    <div class="window error-window">
      <div class="titlebar">
        <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
          <span class="dot dot-close"></span>
          <span class="dot dot-min"></span>
          <span class="dot dot-max"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="title">error — 404</div>
        <div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <Command command="find / -name 'requested_page'" variant="title" />
        
        <Section tone="muted">
          <div class="error-msg">
            <span class="error-code">[ERROR 404]</span>
            <p>La ruta especificada no pudo ser encontrada en el servidor.</p>
            <p>Es posible que el archivo haya sido movido, eliminado o que el comando sea incorrecto.</p>
          </div>
        </Section>

        <div class="separator"></div>

        <div class="actions">
          <p>Sugerencia: Regresa al directorio principal para continuar la exploración.</p>
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
            cd /home/portfolio<span class="cursorish">_</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="status-bar">
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="status-item mode error">ERR</span>
          <span class="status-item file">404_not_found.sh</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .error-window {
    border: 1px solid #ff5f57;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 100px auto;
  }

  .window {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-surface-lowest), var(--color-bg));
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .titlebar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--color-surface-low);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-surface-high);
    padding: 0 16px;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .dot-close { background: #ff5f57; }
  .dot-min   { background: #febc2e; }
  .dot-max   { background: #28c840; }

  .title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .content {
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .error-msg {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .error-code {
    color: #ff5f57;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .separator {
    height: 1px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,95,87,0), rgba(255,95,87,0.35), rgba(255,95,87,0));
  }

  .actions p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #0e0e0e;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    filter: brightness(1.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cursorish {
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  .status-bar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: var(--color-surface-low);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-surface-high);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .status-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .status-item.mode.error {
    background: #ff5f57;
    color: white;
    padding: 0 6px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
